Morocco King Announces Constitution Changes Giving More Power to Lawmakers

-- B y   N a d e e m   H a m i d
-- 
2011-06-17T20:21:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-17/morocco-king-announces-constitution-changes-giving-more-power-to-lawmakers.html
King Mohammed VI of Morocco
announced constitutional ammendments that would change the
governance of the North African nation.  The new constitution will provide more power for the
elected parliament, he said.  The constitutional measures will provide for human rights,
criminalize torture and assure equal rights for women, he said
in a televised address to the nation.  To contact the reporter on this story:
